ygData.subject: ┬┐Freeport┬┐ =)
ygData.msgSnippet: Hello, folks, I ve tried to get my Necro off to Free port about two, three times now.  I get completely lost in High Hold Keep and end up wondering the same
ygData.messageBody:
Hello, folks,

I've tried to get my Necro off to Free port about two, three times
now. I get completely lost in High Hold Keep and end up wondering the same
halls and turns for about an hour or so before I gate back. Could any of
you give the directions to go, to get _out_ the other side of that flaming
place?

Also, do the guards kill you on sight? I'm constantly invis or
finding a room to recast it before it runs out, just in case. :)

Thanks for any help,

~Myskyra / Tunare
